			clear both
			display block
			width 100%
			line-height 1
			vertical-align top
		div
			display block
			font-size 0.8em
			margin-bottom 0.4em*/
		lost-column 1/10 10
		line-height 1.2em
		padding-bottom 1.2em
		word-wrap break-word !important
